Today I continued setting up a TypeScript development environment on Windows 10.

(今天，继续学习在windows10系统中配置好typescript的编程环境。)

First of all, I installed Visual Studio Code.

(首先安装了vs Code.)

I don't plan to install the TypeScript package globally. Instead, I'll install different TypeScript versions inside each project. So I didn't run npm install -g typescript; I first downloaded the `https://github.com/zama-ai/relayer-sdk` project's source files into the project folder.
(My branch: https://github.com/maeganyork/relayer-sdk_my_version)
(我不打算全局安装TypeScript模块，而是打算在不同的项目中安装不同版本的TypeScript模块。因而没有先使用npm命令全局安装TypeScript，而是先下载了`https://github.com/zama-ai/relayer-sdk`项目的源文件到指定的项目文件夹中。)

In root folder: (在项目的根文件夹下：)

npm install @zama-fhe/relayer-sdk
//check
node -e "const p=require('./node_modules/@zama-fhe/relayer-sdk/package.json'); console.log(p.main, p.types, p.name)"
//output:  lib/node.js lib/node.d.ts @zama-fhe/relayer-sdk

src/test.ts:

import { createInstance, SepoliaConfig } from '@zama-fhe/relayer-sdk';

async function main() {
  const instance = await createInstance(SepoliaConfig);
  console.log(instance.getPublicKey())
}

main().catch(console.error);

The ts file must in src folder.(写的测试用的 ts 类型的文件必须放到src文件夹下。)

\\to js file
.\node_modules\.bin\tsc .\src\test.ts

Run js file:

node .\src\test.js

Has errors:

